          Your Ultimate Hub for Guidance and Resources
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Our mission is to provide students, educators, and lifelong learners
          with access to a wealth of educational materials to achieve their
          goals and improve their lives.
        </p>
